# Launch / strategic content — lives in a PRIVATE location (e.g.
# ~/NandaiJarvis/internal-staging/marketing/), NEVER in the public repo.
# Show HN drafts, pre-launch checklists, internal cadence, unpublished
# X threads — all of these reveal pre-announcement strategy and damage
# the launch if visible. Hard guard so no one re-commits this by mistake.
marketing/
launch/
strategy/
